commit.message:
Add name resolution support to toxcore

This finished the name resolution features of tox-named, which will
hopefully replace ToxDNS. Incoming, and outgoing packets are tested and
verified with the auto test.

There are still a few more additions, including, but not limited to packet
resend timeouts, and max number of retrys.
